OL,3,CLabour to drop #28 billion-a-year
OL,4,Cgreen spending pledge
OL,6,FLabour will abandon its policy of
OL,7,Fspending #28 billion a year on
OL,8,Fenvironmental projects in a major U-
OL,9,Fturn.
OL,11,Fan announcement on the party's
OL,12,Fflagship green prosperity plan is due
OL,13,Fto be made on Thursday.
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer is expected to
OL,16,Fconfirm his plan will be scaled back
OL,17,Fdue to changes in the economic
OL,18,Flandscape since it was first unveiled
OL,19,Fin 2021.
