OL,4,Cgreen spending pledge
OL,6,FConfusion over the future of the
OL,7,Fpolicy has grown in recent weeks as
OL,8,Fsome senior figures refused to refer
OL,9,Fto the #28 billion-a-year figure,
OL,10,Fwhile party leader Sir Keir continued
OL,11,Fto do so as recently as Tuesday.
OL,13,Fhas repeatedly declined to recommit to
OL,14,Fthe spending pledge, instead
OL,15,Fhighlighting the need for "iron
OL,16,Fdiscipline" with the public finances.
OL,18,FBut earlier this week, Sir Keir said
OL,19,Fthe money was "desperately needed" for
OL,20,Fthe party's key mission to achieve
OL,21,Fclean power by 2030.
